Subject: Midnight Yoga
Description: During the hustle of Con it is easy to become tense. Relax and recharge with some yoga stretching, whether it is to prepare for sleep or recharge you for a long night of partying.  Open to all levels, abilities, and body types. Wear comfortable clothing and be ready to sweat.    Speakers include:Chloe Zrnich - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
